ray(String)` — combining them passed a `String` to a clause expecting `Array` or `Map`, causing TYPE_MISMATCH (code 53).\n\nSwitching to `LEFT ARRAY JOIN JSONExtractKeys(properties) AS property_key` also resolves the secondary issue from the eval: events with `properties = '{}'` were silently dropped by a plain `ARRAY JOIN` because `JSONExtractKeys('{}')` returns an empty array. `LEFT ARRAY JOIN` preserves these rows, setting `property_key` to `''` (empty string) — which the existing `if (!row.property_key) continue` guard already handles, so those events appear in `event_names` even when they have no properties.\n\n## Known gaps\n\n- HTTP check requires a running dev server + local ClickHouse instance with `.env.local` setting `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD=` (empty) or matching the configured password. This is an environment setup gap, not an implementation issue.\n\n## Issues logged\n\nNone\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01QCsS1MLKk6827cAb7HT27D","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's a summary of what changed:\n\n**Root cause (from eval):** `src/app/api/schema/route.ts:43` combined two conflicting ClickHouse mechanisms — `arrayJoin()` (table function, returns `String` scalars) wrapped inside `ARRAY JOIN` (clause that expects `Array`/`Map`). This caused a TYPE_MISMATCH at runtime.\n\n**Fix:** One-line change — `ARRAY JOIN arrayJoin(JSONExtractKeys(properties)) AS property_key` → `LEFT ARRAY JOIN JSONExtractKeys(properties) AS property_key`\n\nUsing `LEFT ARRAY JOIN` (instead of plain `ARRAY JOIN`) also fixes the secondary issue: events with `properties = '{}'` are no longer silently dropped from `event_names` — the empty-array case now produces a row with `property_key = ''`, which the existing `if (!row.property_key) continue` guard handles correctly.\n\n**Self-eval results:** 94 tests passing, lint clean, type check clean, build clean with `/api/schema` as a Dynamic route."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":896,"cache_read_input_tokens":40909,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":896},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b3920fa5-b870-43b3-878e-187098ea34ee","uuid":"2dd3a83b-b400-43b1-8d69-c15bc5b15b62"}
